wpt.desc: The Black Sculpture by SteveSquirrel (adopted by Delphineous), Traditional Cache (1.5/1.5)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: The Black Sculpture
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: This should be a quick park and grab. The area will probably be quite muggle heavy during normal business hours so please use stealth.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
The local sculptures are one of the things that make Philly a wonderful place for Art. I gave it a 1.5 difficulty due to high muggle activity and stealth being required.

Thank you SteveSquirrel for placing this cache and getting me started on this fun game!

If you scan QR code-style codes, you might be interested in this related hide.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick cache & go. The log is about full.
